#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:33 c7f31abf88d84d35b31b96822e4ed28e
msgid "Create a Label object. It accepts the following parameters:"
msgstr "创建一个 Label 对象。它接受以下参数："

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:35 b078a2da426e4e3592a5fa95c2abe0de
msgid "``text`` is the text to be displayed."
msgstr "``text`` 是要显示的文本。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:36 ../../source/widgets/label.rst:63
#: ca0d6ff4924841aab67ad875c744c0a0 cfad99764d674d38aadb99dd4dae9532
msgid "``x`` is the starting X-axis coordinate displayed."
msgstr "``x`` 为显示的起始 X 轴坐标。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:37 ../../source/widgets/label.rst:64
#: 15a29d70aa764a39b37bc343128580f2 c2d9cb6eb156464489f25782832b2181
msgid "``y`` is the starting Y-axis coordinate displayed."
msgstr "``y`` 为显示的起始 Y 轴坐标。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:38 d12b8791d0d5451180d02c79ce1a931f
msgid "``text_sz`` is the font size for displaying text, usually 1.0."
msgstr "``text_sz`` 是用于显示文本的字体大小，通常为 1.0。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:39 1c48afc1c4b9406f8300cbc2ebc45a4c
msgid "``text_c`` is the font color for displaying text. The default is white."
msgstr "``text_c`` 是用于显示文本的字体颜色。默认值为白色。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:40 ../../source/widgets/label.rst:52
#: 949ff4736ace40a98aff09bf174b8d69 eb754ce6adb2447785bbbe244416facd
msgid "bg_c is the background color of the displayed text, the default is black."
msgstr "bg_c 是显示文本的背景颜色，默认为黑色。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:41 d24a84860eba415c87573331ec0357b8
msgid ""
"``font`` is the set of fonts used to display text. For the built-in "
"fonts, see ``Widgets.FONTS``."
msgstr "``font`` 是用于显示文本的字体集合。对于内置字体，请参见 ``Widgets.FONTS``。"

#: ../../source/widgets/label.rst:42 528965315932419faae2877d97757c45
msgid ""
"parent is the output target of the Label object, the default output is to"
" the LCD, can also be output to the Canvas."
msgstr "parent 是 Label 对象的输出目标，默认输出到 LCD，也可以输出到 Canvas。"

